‘‘Chayime , bhikkhave, dhammā sāraṇīyāsārāṇīyā 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='3', original='sārāṇīyā (sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)', type='auto', previous=', bhikkhave, dhammā sāraṇīyā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='sāraṇīyā'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.', text='sārāṇīyā'}}
. Katame cha? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno mettaṃ kāyakammaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sabrahmacārīsu āvi ceva raho ca, ayampi dhammo sāraṇīyo.

‘‘Chayimā, bhikkhave, nissāraṇīyā dhātuyo. Katamā cha? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya – ‘mettā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā; atha ca pana me byāpādo cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti. So ‘mā heva’ntissa vacanīyo – ‘māyasmā, evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya. Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ mettāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya; atha ca  panassa byāpādo cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatiṭhassatīti 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='16', original='ṭhassatīti (sabbattha) dī. ni. 3.326 passitabbaṃ', type='auto', previous=' panassa byāpādo cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='ṭhassati'}
	Alternative{lang='sabbattha', text='ṭhassatīti'}}
, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, byāpādassa yadidaṃ mettācetovimuttī’timettācetovimutti 
